---
---

<figure class="verdict-mock" aria-label="A mock of the ChatOBD2 verdict card UI surface">
  <header class="verdict-mock__head">
    <span class="verdict-mock__eyebrow">Product surface</span>
    <h3 class="verdict-mock__title">What a scan returns</h3>
  </header>

  <div class="verdict-mock__frame">
    <!-- Phone-frame style mock -->
    <div class="vm__device">
      <div class="vm__device-bar">
        <span class="vm__device-time">9:41</span>
        <span class="vm__device-pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="vm__device-status">connected · 2014 Civic</span>
      </div>

      <div class="vm__bubble vm__bubble--user">
        <span class="vm__bubble-meta">You</span>
        <p>Run a scan. Anything I should worry about?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="vm__card">
        <div class="vm__safe-bar">
          <span class="vm__safe-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="vm__safe-label">Safe to drive</span>
          <span class="vm__safe-tier">Monitor</span>
        </div>

        <div class="vm__confidence">
          <span class="vm__confidence-label">Scan confidence</span>
          <div class="vm__confidence-bar" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="vm__confidence-fill"></span>
          </div>
          <span class="vm__confidence-value">Solid · 14 PIDs</span>
        </div>

        <div class="vm__verdict">
          <span class="vm__verdict-eyebrow">Verdict</span>
          <h4 class="vm__verdict-headline">One pending code, no immediate action</h4>
          <p class="vm__verdict-summary">
            P0420 (catalyst efficiency) is logged but not active. Drivetrain
            pulled clean across two cycles. Re-scan in 200 mi.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="vm__findings">
          <span class="vm__findings-eyebrow">What matters most</span>
          <ul class="vm__findings-list">
            <li>
              <span class="vm__finding-tier vm__finding-tier--monitor"></span>
              <span class="vm__finding-code">P0420</span>
              <span class="vm__finding-name">Catalyst efficiency below threshold</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="vm__finding-tier vm__finding-tier--ok"></span>
              <span class="vm__finding-code">12 systems</span>
              <span class="vm__finding-name">Healthy across drivetrain &amp; emissions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <button class="vm__action" type="button">
          <span class="vm__action-label">Explain P0420 in plain language</span>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="vm__followups" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="vm__chip">Is this getting worse?</span>
        <span class="vm__chip">Cost to fix?</span>
        <span class="vm__chip">Will it fail emissions?</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="verdict-mock__notes">
      <span class="verdict-mock__notes-eyebrow">Why it's structured</span>
      <ol class="verdict-mock__notes-list">
        <li>Safe-to-drive answer comes <strong>first</strong>, before any text.</li>
        <li>Confidence is <strong>part of the answer</strong>. Partial scans say so.</li>
        <li>Findings are <strong>tier-coded</strong>, instead of a flat list of acronyms.</li>
        <li>Next action is <strong>one tap</strong>. No prompt-writing required.</li>
      </ol>
    </aside>
  </div>
</figure>

<style>
  .verdict-mock {
    margin: var(--space-12) 0;
  }

  .verdict-mock__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .verdict-mock__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
  }

  .verdict-mock__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .verdict-mock__frame {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 820px) {
    .verdict-mock__frame {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 360px) 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  /* Device shell */
  .vm__device {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    background-color: #0A0A0C;
    border: 1px solid #18181B;
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    color: #FAFAFA;
  }

  .vm__device-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.55);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .vm__device-time {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.85);
  }

  .vm__device-pulse {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #10B981;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px #10B981;
    margin: 0 4px;
    animation: pulse-dot 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .vm__device-status {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* Chat bubble */
  .vm__bubble {
    align-self: flex-end;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 16px 16px 4px 16px;
    background-color: #1F1F23;
    color: #FAFAFA;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 86%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .vm__bubble--user {
    background-color: #2A2A30;
  }

  .vm__bubble-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 9px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.4);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* The verdict card itself */
  .vm__card {
    align-self: stretch;
    background-color: #14141A;
    border: 1px solid #232329;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  /* Safe-to-drive bar */
  .vm__safe-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12), rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.04));
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .vm__safe-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #F59E0B;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.6);
  }

  .vm__safe-label {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FAFAFA;
  }

  .vm__safe-tier {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #F59E0B;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
  }

  /* Confidence */
  .vm__confidence {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 4px 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .vm__confidence-label {
    grid-row: 1;
    grid-column: 1;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .vm__confidence-value {
    grid-row: 1;
    grid-column: 2;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #10B981;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .vm__confidence-bar {
    grid-row: 2;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    height: 4px;
    background-color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.08);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .vm__confidence-fill {
    display: block;
    width: 84%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4), #10B981);
    border-radius: inherit;
  }

  /* Verdict text */
  .vm__verdict {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .vm__verdict-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .vm__verdict-headline {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FAFAFA;
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .vm__verdict-summary {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.65);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Findings */
  .vm__findings {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.06);
  }

  .vm__findings-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .vm__findings-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .vm__findings-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 4px auto 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .vm__finding-tier {
    width: 4px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background-color: #F59E0B;
  }

  .vm__finding-tier--ok { background-color: #10B981; }

  .vm__finding-code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FAFAFA;
  }

  .vm__finding-name {
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.7);
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Next action button */
  .vm__action {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: #F59E0B;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 150ms;
  }

  .vm__action:hover {
    background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.14);
  }

  /* Follow-up chips */
  .vm__followups {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .vm__chip {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background-color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.1);
    color: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  /* Right-side notes */
  .verdict-mock__notes {
    align-self: start;
    padding: var(--space-5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }

  .verdict-mock__notes-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .verdict-mock__notes-list {
    counter-reset: vm-notes;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .verdict-mock__notes-list li {
    counter-increment: vm-notes;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 28px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .verdict-mock__notes-list li::before {
    content: counter(vm-notes, decimal-leading-zero);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .verdict-mock__notes-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
